{"tha-ap291:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap291:0.2":"Pannadayakavagga ","tha-ap291:0.3":"9 Buddhupatthayikattheraapadana ","tha-ap291:1.1":"“Vetambhiniti me namam, ","tha-ap291:1.2":"pitusantam mamam tada; ","tha-ap291:1.3":"Mama hattham gahetvana, ","tha-ap291:1.4":"upanayi mahamunim. ","tha-ap291:2.1":"Imemam uddisissanti, ","tha-ap291:2.2":"buddha lokagganayaka; ","tha-ap291:2.3":"Teham upatthim sakkaccam, ","tha-ap291:2.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap291:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap291:3.2":"buddhe upatthahim tada; ","tha-ap291:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap291:3.4":"upatthanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap291:4.1":"Tevisamhi ito kappe, ","tha-ap291:4.2":"caturo asu khattiya; ","tha-ap291:4.3":"Samanupatthaka nama, ","tha-ap291:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap291:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap291:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap291:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap291:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma buddhupatthayiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap291:7.1":"Buddhupatthayikattherassapadanam navamam. "}